Description: Sparebanken Sor is a Norway-based independent savings bank, that offers a broad range of banking and investment products to its customers. Its principal customers are private households and small and medium-sized enterprises. The Banks main market is located in the counties of Agder and Telemark. The Bank provides financial services for its customers such as health and property insurance, travel insurance, loans and mortgage, car loans, card issuer, mobile and online banking services, international payment, saving and pension savings among other. Its main office is locat-ed in Kristiansand.
